    "In the case of social media, hashtags can be used to obtain datasets in certain dialects.",
    "Kuparinen [2023] take advantage of dialect awareness week in Finland.",
    "They use a hashtag indicating usage of dialects in order to collect tweets in different dialects of Finnish.",
    "In the context of Arabic dialect tweets, Boujou et al. [2021] benchmark is a novel dataset of 50,000 tweets for five dialects of Arabic-Algerian, Lebanon, Morocco, Tunisian, and Egyptian.4.2.4 Location.",
